tags: [[Loading Source JSON]]
title: Drag and Drop
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Drop a file onto the source textarea (or its dropzone wrapper) and the contents appear in place.

The plugin intercepts drops in the capturing phase so TiddlyWiki's own drag-and-drop importer doesn't try to ingest the file as a tiddler.  Dropping inside the source area always means //"use this as source JSON"//, not //"import this into the wiki."//
